based modeling approach carried out here is the capability
to estimate fBLR. For a disk like BLR, (see Collin et al. 2006;
Li et al. 2013; Rakshit et al. 2015) fBLR can be written as"
fBLR ≈ (sin2 θopn + sin2 θinc)−1 (14)
"where θinc is the inclination angle and θopn is the open-
